commit_list.message:
fixed global.cpp to kde4

KSharedConfig::openConfig now returns a smart pointer KSharedConfig::Ptr. So Global::config() is now converted to an smart pointer cast down to regular
pointer. This will work, just not a good idea. Also KAction->icon() no longer returns a QString but instead returns a KIcon. Using QVariant, I
forcefully cast it to a QString b/c I am not sure what openNoteIcon() does. Eventually, I will need to come back and clean this up also.
